               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17670429-37-off209-c237" targOrder="Y" targets="t17670429-37-defend315 t17670429-37-off209 t17670429-37-verdict211"></join>
         
               <p>230. (L.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17670429-37-defend315" type="defendantName">
                     William 
                     Mason 
                  <interp inst="t17670429-37-defend315" type="surname" value="Mason"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-defend315" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-defend315" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17670429-37-off209" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-off209" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-off209" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a woollen surtout coat, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17670429-37-victim317" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Thomas 
                  <interp inst="t17670429-37-victim317" type="surname" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-victim317" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-victim317" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17670429-37-off209 t17670429-37-victim317"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17670429-37-cd210" type="crimeDate">March. 6</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17670429-37-off209 t17670429-37-cd210"></join>. ||</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17670429-37-person318">
                  John 
                  Thomas 
               <interp inst="t17670429-37-person318" type="surname" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-person318" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-person318" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lost a surtout coat from off a box by my bed-side, on the 6th of March. On the Monday morning I went and found it at Mr. Paterson's, a pawnbroker; I took up the prisoner; he confessed before the Alderman he was in distress, and he took it, and thought to have brought it back again.</p>
               <p>Coterill, servant to Mr. Paterson, deposed he lent the prisoner 18 d. upon the coat. (Produced and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence.</p>
               <p>I did not take it with a design to keep it.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17670429-37-verdict211" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-verdict211" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>. <rs id="t17670429-37-punish212" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17670429-37-punish212" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17670429-37-defend315 t17670429-37-punish212"></join>
               T
            </rs>.</p>
            </div1>
